issue.body:
It's that time of year again! Go 1.11 is released, let's use it.

This PR also:
* removes our archive/tar fork (since upstream archive/tar is fixed for static builds, and osusergo build tag is set in PR #37500);
* removes `ENV GO_VERSION` from Dockerfile (not needed since PR #37592);
* reformats sources with `gofmt -s` from go 1.11 to avoid validation errors;
* Revendor ugorji/go to include a backported fix (https://github.com/kolyshkin/ugorji-go/commit/1cf431c13dec46596)

